Package: gsDesignCRT
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Group Sequential Design for Cluster Randomized Trials
Authors@R: person(given = "Lee", family = "Ding", email =
          "lee_ding@g.harvard.edu", role = c('aut','cre'))
Description: Derives group sequential cluster randomized trial designs with
    continuous or binary outcomes. Based on the methods described in
    Jennison, Christopher and Turnbull, Bruce W., 2000,
    "Group Sequential Methods with Applications to Clinical Trials" and
    implemented in the package gsDesign.
    ISBN: 0-8493-0316-8.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
